OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773436323
OL,3,CUK's largest AI data centre plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FPlans for UK's biggest AI data centre
OL,7,Fhave been approved by councillors in
OL,8,FNorth Lincolnshire.
OL,10,FThe development at the former RAF
OL,11,FElsham Wolds, near Brigg, which could
OL,12,Fcreate around 900 jobs in the area,
OL,13,Fwould be about the size of 300
OL,14,Ffootball pitches.
OL,16,FIt will house computing infrastructure
OL,17,Fneeded to power artificial
OL,18,Fintelligence, cloud computing and high-
OL,19,Fperformance data processing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
