FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773436323
OL,3,CUK's largest AI data centre plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FNorth Lincolnshire Council leader Rob
OL,7,FWaltham said: "The numbers attached to
OL,8,Fthis project are eye-watering ` almost
OL,9,Fhard to get your head around. But what
OL,10,Freally matters is what it means for
OL,11,Fresidents in North Lincolnshire.
OL,13,F"This will bring thousands of
OL,14,Fconstruction jobs, hundreds of highly
OL,15,Fskilled, high-paid long-term roles,
OL,16,Fand the chance to build a new industry
OL,17,Fright here in North Lincolnshire.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773436323
OL,3,CUK's largest AI data centre plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,F"This is a once-in-a-generation
OL,7,Finvestment opportunity. North
OL,8,FLincolnshire remains a place where
OL,9,Fmajor industries choose to invest,
OL,10,Fgrow and create jobs."
OL,12,FConstruction is expected to begin in
OL,13,F2027 with the first phase opening in
OL,14,F2029.
OL,16,FThe decade-long building project is
OL,17,Fexpected to create around 1,000
OL,18,Fconstruction jobs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
