PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773436323
OL,3,CUK's largest AI data centre plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FGreystoke, the company behind the
OL,7,Fplans, says the plant will "help meet
OL,8,Fa critical UK need for data centre
OL,9,Finfrastructure" and that the site will
OL,10,Fform part of a proposed network of AI
OL,11,Fdata centre campuses across North
OL,12,FLincolnshire.
OL,14,FThe company said it intends to create
OL,15,Ffour sites generating 2.5GW of AI
OL,16,Fcomputing power, bringing more than
OL,17,F#20 billion of investment to the
OL,18,Fregion.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
